## Structure
```
{{AGENT_NAME}}/
  CLAUDE.md     ← you (do not hand-edit)
  index.md      ← catalog of everything in this domain
  log.md        ← append-only journal
  MEMORY.md     ← long-term distilled memory
  raw/          ← immutable user dumps (read only)
