## Bus protocol
When the `UserPromptSubmit` hook or `/inbox` signals an incoming message:
1. Read the file in `vault/bus/to/{{AGENT_LC}}/`.
2. Do what it asks (or record why it's deferred).
3. Append a `log.md` entry.
4. Move the file to `vault/bus/sent/done__<original-name>.md` (exact original name).

If you detect a cross-domain situation, **send a bus message yourself** (don't wait):
`<repo>/core/bus/send.sh --to <agent> --from {{AGENT_LC}} --title "..." --body "..."`

